"https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Matt-Berninger-of-The-National.-Credit-Craig-Barritt_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="国民的马特·贝宁格（Matt Berninger）。信用 - 克雷格·巴里特/盖蒂图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Matt-Berninger-of-The-National.-Credit-Craig-Barritt_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Matt-Berninger-of-The-National.-Credit-Craig-Barritt_Getty-Images-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Matt-Berninger-of-The-National.-Credit-Craig-Barritt_Getty-Images-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Matt-Berninger-of-The-National.-Credit-Craig-Barritt_Getty-Images-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Matt-Berninger-of-The-National.-Credit-Craig-Barritt_Getty-Images-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Matt-Berninger-of-The-National.-Credit-Craig-Barritt_Getty-Images-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-berninger">马特·贝宁格（Matt Berninger）</a>首次演奏了他的独奏材料，并在利兹的演出中播出了他的新专辑“ Get Sunk”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">国民</a>主持人于2020年发行了他的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/matt-berninger-serpentine-prison-review-2784479">《蛇形监狱》</a> ，但由于Covid而无法进行任何曲目。他的新专辑“ Get Sunk”将于5月30日通过Concord/Book Records到达。<a href="https://found.ee/MB-GetSunk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处预订新专辑</a>。</p><p>贝宁格（Berninger）现在在4月2日至3日在利兹的布鲁德内尔社交俱乐部（Brudenell Social Club）上演出了两场亲密的，售罄的节目，在那里他第一次现场表演了独奏材料，包括他即将发行的专辑中未发行的片段。</p><p>他播放的一些歌曲包括“内陆海洋”的现场首次亮相，“闯入表演”，“垃圾”，“再来一秒钟”和“ Litter By Litter”。他还演奏了国民的曲目“福音”。在下面的Leeds Show上观看一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matt-berninger">berninger</a>表演的镜头。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgr