gle was incoming recently by sending a text message to their mailing list. “You guys ready for another[?]” it read. They then shared a video on TikTok, revealing that there would be a “new song tease this week.”</p><p> Haim are yet to announce their fourth studio album, which will follow 2020&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/haim-women-in-music-pt-iii-album-review-2688128">&#39;Women In Music Pt. III&#39;</a> . During a recent interview, the trio revealed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haims-new-album-features-an-as-yet-uncleared-george-michael-sample-inspired-by-beyonce-3845935">the record would feature an as-yet-uncleared sample of George Michael&#39;s &#39;Freedom! &#39;90&#39;</a> .</p><p> The track in question, titled &#39;Gone&#39;, is the opening track to the new LP, and reportedly captures the feeling of clarity after a break-up. The record will also contain a song called &#39;Take Me Back&#39;. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="HAIM - Relationships (Official Video)" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dOI_QTmK8Ks?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Alana Haim told <a href="https://i-d.co/article/haim-relationships-single-interview/"><i>ID</i></a> that the upcoming album was “the closest we&#39;ve ever gotten to how we wanted to sound”, adding that it was a “completely different experience” recording this time around.</p><p> Haim once again worked with producer Rostam Batmanglij ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Vampire-Weekend">Vampire Weekend</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artsits/Clairo">Clairo</a> ) on the record.</p><p> “Working with Rostam, in general it&#39;s very quick, kinetic with him, which I really love as an artist,” Danielle explained. “Maybe before, it wasn&#39;t that way, it was kind of a more… longer, searching, laboured situation.”</p><p> In other news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-join-the-line-up-for-radio-1s-big-weekend-2025-3849312">Haim have been added to the line-up for Radio 1&#39;s Big Weekend 2025</a> . The event is set to take place at Sefton Park in Liverpool next month. The group are also scheduled to make appearances at <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-2025-line-up-announced-tickets-3805796#:~:text=Primavera%20Sound%20have%20announced%20the,Carpenter%20all%20set%20to%20headline.">Primavera Sound in Barcelona</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-porto-announce-stacked-2025-line-up-3810606">Porto</a> this summer.</p><p> Meanwhile, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bon-iver-drops-new-singles-if-only-i-could-wait-featuring-danielle-haim-and-walk-home-3846459">Danielle Haim has teamed up with Bon Iver on his new single &#39;If Only I Could Wait&#39;</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haims-danielle-on-new-single-everybodys-trying-to-figure-me-out-writing-it-has-gotten-me-through-some-hard-times-3851714">HAIM&#39;s Danielle on new single &#39;Everybody&#39;s Trying to Figure Me Out&#39;: “Writing it has gotten me through some hard times”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
